21:43.053 --> 21:47.891
(metal door clangs open)
(door closes)

21:48.600 --> 21:50.686
(door locks clang shut)
(siren blares)

21:50.686 --> 21:51.812
CHIEF ENGINEER:
Pipes started shaking,

21:51.812 --> 21:53.063
so I reduced the speed.

21:53.063 --> 21:54.857
-And?
-Problem's coming from in there.

21:54.857 --> 21:56.191
(sizzle)
(chief engineer gasps)

21:56.984 --> 21:58.110
It's hot to the touch.

21:58.110 --> 21:59.820
I wouldn't venture in there.

21:59.820 --> 22:02.698
My guess is cracked steam pipes
and a cocktail of
superheated oil.

22:02.698 --> 22:04.908
That room is probably
700 degrees.

22:04.908 --> 22:06.243
We need to shut her
down, Captain.

22:06.243 --> 22:07.494
Let the engineers do their work.

22:07.494 --> 22:08.704
No.

22:08.704 --> 22:10.330
Reduce speed to 15 knots.

22:10.455 --> 22:13.917
-Captain, it only takes
a spark from...
- All that clatter down here,

22:13.917 --> 22:15.669
