22:15.836 --> 22:18.255
I said do not stop.

22:18.505 --> 22:21.091
By all means, find
a way to reduce
the pressure and speed.

22:21.091 --> 22:22.134
Gradually.

22:22.134 --> 22:23.969
But do not stop.

22:24.511 --> 22:28.223
And the next time you decide
to slow my ship without
my consent,

22:28.724 --> 22:30.267
I'll leave you at
the nearest port.

22:30.267 --> 22:31.435
Yes, Captain.

