(camera clicks)

23:53.225 --> 23:54.393
(metal turnstile cranks)

23:55.185 --> 23:56.144
(eerie music)

23:57.980 --> 23:58.939
(footsteps running)

24:07.614 --> 24:08.991
(water splashing)

24:11.451 --> 24:12.411
Hello?

24:12.870 --> 24:13.954
JACKIE: Down here.

24:20.711 --> 24:21.712
(tense music)

24:24.339 --> 24:25.340
(camera shutter clicks)

24:27.759 --> 24:36.935
(pages flip)

24:36.935 --> 24:38.896
I didn't know there still was
a ship's Captain.

24:38.896 --> 24:41.481
There is not.
But don't tell anyone.

24:42.482 --> 24:43.442
(scoffs)

24:44.067 --> 24:45.944
I just like the suit.

24:45.944 --> 24:49.823
(Anne chuckles)
So, why a book about
us, exactly?

24:49.823 --> 24:51.575
I am a digital marketing
consultant...
(phone rings)

24:51.575 --> 24:52.993
and my...

24:52.993 --> 24:54.953
...my son is obsessed
with ghost stories.

24:54.953 --> 24:56.955
(phone rings repeatedly)
A little too obsessed
actually and...

24:57.080 --> 24:58.790
MAN:Bittner, are you there?
