24:59.082 --> 25:00.834
Well, er, one day
he has this dream
and he says to me,

25:00.834 --> 25:02.920
"Mom, I had a dream
that I was on The Queen Mary."

25:02.920 --> 25:04.880
And I was like,
"Oh, you know, we
should go visit."

25:05.255 --> 25:08.342
And he said,
"No, I had a dream
we lived there."

25:08.634 --> 25:09.843
(laughs)

25:11.178 --> 25:12.262
Not kidding.

25:12.638 --> 25:14.389
And so, you know, it
got me thinking,

25:14.556 --> 25:18.185
um, what about doing a book
from a child's perspective?

25:18.185 --> 25:22.105
-Hmm.
-Exploring the ship
and some of the...

25:23.315 --> 25:24.650
stranger stories.

25:25.400 --> 25:28.195
-Ghost stories?
-Yes, the ghost stories.

25:29.613 --> 25:32.658
