ship's rich history

25:32.658 --> 25:35.619
and we could raise awareness
and we could help save it.

25:37.996 --> 25:39.998
I didn't know we needed saving.

25:40.958 --> 25:42.459
Just what I see in the media.

25:44.586 --> 25:45.629
Stories.

25:46.004 --> 25:47.422
Right. Stories.

25:50.968 --> 25:53.095
You know, we're pretty
used to stories
around here,

25:53.095 --> 25:57.391
