28:21.118 --> 28:23.495
BITTNER: People came here
to enjoy glamour.

28:23.954 --> 28:24.955
They still do.

28:25.289 --> 28:27.207
We host brunch on Sundays.

28:27.207 --> 28:29.209
Wedding receptions.
Corporate parties.

28:29.418 --> 28:31.336
You know, Bar-mitzvahs
and what-not.

28:32.337 --> 28:33.630
Oh, throughout the voyage,

28:34.131 --> 28:37.885
er, those ships marked
The Queen's Mary's
location along the Atlantic.

28:38.135 --> 28:42.681
Unfortunately, they
stopped working
after we permanently
docked in '67.

28:42.681 --> 28:46.226
We could capture these
fascinating details
in a wholly original way.

28:46.977 --> 28:48.770
Well, other people have
taken pictures.

28:48.770 --> 28:50.898
How do you propose
your book will be any different?

28:51.565 --> 28:53.942
The quality of the work
and the story you tell
with the pictures,

28:53.942 --> 28:55.736
that's all very important.
But...

28:56.069 --> 28:57.863
