29:30.604 --> 29:32.272
Thank you, Miss Calder.

29:32.272 --> 29:35.317
I'll, er, pass this
along to Mr Torres
and we'll get back to you.

29:35.317 --> 29:36.693
(footsteps receding)

29:36.818 --> 29:37.945
