He seems traumatised.

30:00.467 --> 30:03.679
I just...sorry, I turned around,
he was just gone and I ...

30:05.305 --> 30:06.640
How'd the meeting go?

30:06.640 --> 30:08.058
Fine.

30:08.058 --> 30:10.185
Um, I was thinking,
if this book thing goes well,

30:10.310 --> 30:11.562
