to another town
and shut me out.

30:35.752 --> 30:37.838
ANNE: Stop it, it's way overdue
we all moved on.

30:37.838 --> 30:41.049
PATRICK: I, I hear what
you're saying,
but it's a house, not a prison.

30:41.049 --> 30:42.217
(deck creaking)
ANNE: You always made it feel

30:42.217 --> 30:44.052
so God damn permanent.

30:44.678 --> 30:46.722
GWEN: Jackie, darling.

30:47.181 --> 30:49.224
(distorted) If I'm doing that I,
