you stay here forever.

31:05.449 --> 31:07.659
(distorted) Honey, are you okay?

31:07.784 --> 31:09.661
GWEN: Wait for us there.

31:09.661 --> 31:11.496
(quickened footsteps)

31:11.496 --> 31:15.167
GWEN: And we'll be
a family again.

31:15.334 --> 31:17.294
We found him. No big deal.

31:17.294 --> 31:19.379
-He's wet.
-Yeah, I can see that.

31:19.588 --> 31:21.340
You know, but otherwise
unharmed.

31:21.340 --> 31:23.050
ANNE: (distorted) Come on,
let's get you home and dry.

31:23.175 --> 31:24.468
You poor thing.
(voices talking over)

31:24.676 --> 31:27.638
BITTNER: (distorted)
Miss Calder!
Wait, wait! Miss Calder!

31:30.265 --> 31:32.392
(elevator door closes)

31:34.728 --> 31:37.189
(scream)
(glass smashes)

31:41.443 --> 31:43.111
(phone ringing)

31:44.112 --> 31:46.114
(beep)
BITTNER:Miss Calder?
Charles Bittner.

31:46.114 --> 31:47.157
Good news.

31:47.157 --> 31:49.243
We'd like you and your
family to come back

31:49.243 --> 31:51.161
